title: Meghan Markle laughs off awkward moment after awards ceremony mix-up
text:
Meghan Markle laughs off awkward moment after awards ceremony mix-up Friday, February 02, 2018 - 00:38 
Britain's Prince Harry's fiancée Meghan Markle laughed off an awkward moment during the Endeavour Fund Awards ceremony on Thursday (February 1) evening. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
